import EmploymentHistoryModel from '../models/EmploymentHistoryModel'
import SkillsModel from '../models/SkillsModel'
import EducationModels from '../models/EducationModels'
export default class CvModels {
    id: string | null;
    jobTitle: string | null
    fileImage: string | null
    firstName: string | null
    lastName: number | null
    email: string | null
    phone: string | null
    country: string | null
    city: string | null
    address: string | null
    postalCode: string | null
    drivingLicense: string | null
    nationality: string | null
    placeOfBirth: string | null
    dateOfBirth: string | null
    summary: string | null
    listEmployment: EmploymentHistoryModel[]
    listSkills: SkillsModel[]
    listEducation: EducationModels[]
    constructor () {
      this.id = null
      this.jobTitle = null
      this.fileImage = null
      this.firstName = null
      this.lastName = null
      this.email = null
      this.phone = null
      this.country = null
      this.city = null
      this.address = null
      this.postalCode = null
      this.drivingLicense = null
      this.nationality = null
      this.placeOfBirth = null
      this.dateOfBirth = null
      this.summary = null
      this.listEmployment = []
      this.listSkills = []
      this.listEducation = []
    }
}
